<tr id="L83"><td><a href="#L83">83</a></td><td>APOLLO [on viewscreen]:  hat was your first lesson. Remember it. Captain Kirk, I invite you and your officers to join me. But do not bring that one, the one with the pointed ears. He is much like Pan, and Pan always bored me. No sad faces. This is a time to rejoice, not to fear. You are returning home. Let your hearts prepare to sing.</td></tr>

