<tr id="L156"><td><a href="#L156">156</a></td><td>APOLLO:  Agamemnon was one such as you, and Hercules. Pride and arrogance. They defied me until they felt my wrath.</td></tr>

<tr id="L157"><td><a href="#L157">157</a></td><td>SCOTT:  I would like to point out that we are quite capable of some wrath ourselves.</td></tr>

